# Insight distillation redact list (additional sanitizer patterns)
# 1 line per pattern. Lines starting with '#' are comments.
# Each non-empty line is compiled as a JavaScript RegExp with the 'g' flag.
# Matches are replaced with [REDACTED] before any insight is persisted or
# sent to the LLM.
#
# Default sanitizers (already applied): API keys (sk-, ghp_, AKIA, etc.),
# JWTs, PEM private keys, Authorization Bearer headers, and .env-style lines.
# Add project-specific patterns below.
#
# Examples:
#   internal-corp-id-\d+
#   acme-customer-[A-Z0-9]+
#   https://[a-z0-9.-]+\.internal\.example/\S*
#
# This file is created once by chezmoi and is never overwritten by subsequent
# applies. Edit freely.
